<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Fellowship — AI Agent Orchestration</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Fellowship orchestrates AI coding agents with specs, reviews, and memory — so you ship better code, faster." />
  <meta property="og:title" content="Fellowship — AI Agent Orchestration" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Define teams of AI agents. Auto-generate specs. Writer-Reviewer pattern. Built-in memory." />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/logo.png" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
